FBIS3-53069 "drnes007_k_94006" FBIS-NES-94-007 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Jan 1994 IRAQ Clandestine Reports Minister Threatens Kuwait NC1001174594 (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan in Arabic 1500 GMT 10 Jan 94 NC1001174594 (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan in Arabic 1500 GMT 10 Jan 94 Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] The AL-MU'TAMAR [Iraqi opposition newspaper] newspaper, citing some sources, has reported that the regime's defense minister, 'Ali Hasan al-Majid, threatened the Kuwaitis during a meeting with tribal chiefs in the city of al-Batha', which is located between al-Nasiriyah and Sinawah, on 25 December. Al-Majid emphasized that Saddam and his henchmen will reoccupy Kuwait.
